  '(--use-annotation -an)'{--use-annotation,-an}'[The names of the annotations which should used for calculations]:value:' \
  '(--truth-sensitivity-tranche -tranche)'{--truth-sensitivity-tranche,-tranche}'[The levels of truth sensitivity at which to slice the data. (in percent, that is 1.0 fo...]:value:' \
  '--ignore-filter[If specified, the variant recalibrator will also use variants marked as filtered by the...]' \
  '--ignore-all-filters[If specified, the variant recalibrator will ignore all input filters. Useful to rerun t...]' \
